snippet: Thierry Henry had a goal and two assists for the Red Bulls, who climbed into a first-place tie with the Impact in the Eastern Conference of Major League Soccer.
abstract: New York Red Bulls shutout Montreal Impact with 4-0 victory in Major League Soccer.
